<span class="displaytext">milford, nh -- new mexico governor (candidate full) today released the following statement on the resignation of idaho senator larry craig:<p>"senator craig's resignation was the right thing to do. dragging out this process and diverting the attention of the american people to personal matters would not have been appropriate conduct.</p><p>"now we can get back to the domestic and international problems that our country faces. let us end the war in iraq. let us fix our economy and provide good-paying jobs for our hard-working citizens. let us provide health care for every american. these are the issues our nation should be tackling."</p></span>



